object.customQuery:
WITH current_batch AS (
    SELECT 
        bls.batch_id,
        bls.source_start_cutoff_datetime,
        bls.source_end_cutoff_datetime
    FROM $$operational_schema.batch_load_summary bls
    WHERE bls.source_system_code = '$$sourcesystemcode'
      AND bls.batch_status = 'Inprogress'
      AND bls.batch_id = (
          SELECT MAX(batch_id)
          FROM $$operational_schema.batch_load_summary
          WHERE source_system_code = '$$sourcesystemcode'
            AND batch_status = 'Inprogress'
			AND target_schema_name = '$$refined_schema'
			AND target_table_name = '$$target_table_name'
      )
) 
select
distinct 
'' as predictive_analytics_assessment_summary_id,
'ACX' as predictive_analytics_assessment_summary_source_system,
'Analytics' as predictive_analytics_assessment_summary_domain,
--aeas.cmm_container as predictive_analytics_assessment_summary_type,  
 CASE
    WHEN aeas.cmm_container is not null or aeas.cmm_container <> ''            
    THEN aeas.cmm_container 
    else NULL
END  AS predictive_analytics_assessment_summary_type,
aeas.originating_source_name as originating_source_name,
aeas.originating_load_type as originating_load_type,
cb.batch_id  as predictive_analytics_assessment_summary_batch_id,
'' as predictive_analytics_assessment_summary_row_effective_start_datetime,
'' as predictive_analytics_assessment_summary_row_effective_end_datetime,
'' as predictive_analytics_assessment_summary_row_status,
paas.predictive_analytics_assessment_summary_row_md5checksum,
aeas.acx_ea_assessment_summary_row_md5checksum,
'' as predictive_analytics_assessment_summary_row_created_by,
'' as predictive_analytics_assessment_summary_row_modified_by,
'' as predictive_analytics_assessment_summary_row_load_state,

--aeas.id as predictive_analytics_assessment_summary_row_source_system_key,
 CASE
    WHEN aeas.id is not null or aeas.id <> ''            
    THEN aeas.id 
    else NULL
END  AS predictive_analytics_assessment_summary_row_source_system_key,

--aeas.system_id  as source_system_system_id, 
 CASE
    WHEN aeas.system_id is not null         
    THEN aeas.system_id 
    else NULL
END  AS source_system_system_id,


--aeas.parent_id as source_system_parent_id,
 CASE
    WHEN aeas.parent_id is not null or aeas.parent_id <> ''            
    THEN aeas.parent_id 
    else NULL
END  AS source_system_parent_id,


--aeas.assessment_id as assessment_id,
 CASE
    WHEN aeas.assessment_id is not null or aeas.assessment_id <> ''            
    THEN aeas.assessment_id 
    else NULL
END  AS assessment_id,


--aeas.solution_id as solution_id,
 CASE
    WHEN aeas.solution_id is not null or aeas.solution_id <> ''            
    THEN aeas.solution_id 
    else NULL
END  AS solution_id,


--aeas.solution_name as solution_name,
 CASE
    WHEN aeas.solution_name is not null or aeas.solution_name <> ''            
    THEN aeas.solution_name 
    else NULL
END  AS solution_name,


--aeas.business_function as business_function,
 CASE
    WHEN aeas.business_function is not null or aeas.business_function <> ''            
    THEN aeas.business_function 
    else NULL
END  AS business_function,


--aeas.assessed_entity as assessed_entity,
 CASE
    WHEN aeas.assessed_entity is not null or aeas.assessed_entity <> ''            
    THEN aeas.assessed_entity 
    else NULL
END  AS assessed_entity,


--aeas.category as assessment_category,
 CASE
    WHEN aeas.category is not null or aeas.category <> ''            
    THEN aeas.category 
    else NULL
END  AS assessment_category,


--aeas.score as assessment_score,
 CASE
    WHEN aeas.score is not null or aeas.score <> ''            
    THEN aeas.score 
    else NULL
END  AS assessment_score,

--aeas.score_percentile as assessment_score_percentile,
 CASE
    WHEN aeas.score_percentile is not null or aeas.score_percentile <> ''            
    THEN aeas.score_percentile 
    else NULL
END  AS assessment_score_percentile,

--aeas.normalized_score as assessment_normalized_score,
 CASE
    WHEN aeas.normalized_score is not null or aeas.normalized_score <> ''            
    THEN aeas.normalized_score 
    else NULL
END  AS assessment_normalized_score,

--aeas.recommended_action_description as assessment_recommended_action_description,
 CASE
    WHEN aeas.recommended_action_description is not null or aeas.recommended_action_description <> ''            
    THEN aeas.recommended_action_description 
    else NULL
END  AS assessment_recommended_action_description,

--aeas.recommended_action_code as assessment_recommended_action_code,
 CASE
    WHEN aeas.recommended_action_code is not null or aeas.recommended_action_code <> ''            
    THEN aeas.recommended_action_code 
    else NULL
END  AS assessment_recommended_action_code,


--aeas.conclusion_description  as assessment_conclusion_description,
 CASE
    WHEN aeas.conclusion_description is not null or aeas.conclusion_description <> ''            
    THEN aeas.conclusion_description 
    else NULL
END  AS assessment_conclusion_description,


--aeas.conclusion_code  as assessment_conclusion_code,
 CASE
    WHEN aeas.conclusion_code is not null or aeas.conclusion_code <> ''            
    THEN aeas.conclusion_code 
    else NULL
END  AS assessment_conclusion_code,


--aeas.score_date as assessment_score_date,  
 CASE
    WHEN aeas.score_date is not null or aeas.score_date <> ''            
    THEN aeas.score_date 
    else NULL
END  AS assessment_score_date,


--aeas.assesment_detail as assesment_detail,
 CASE
    WHEN aeas.assesment_detail is not null or aeas.assesment_detail <> ''            
    THEN aeas.assesment_detail 
    else NULL
END  AS assesment_detail,

--aeas.error as assessment_error,  
 CASE
    WHEN aeas.error is not null or aeas.error <> ''            
    THEN aeas.error 
    else NULL
END  AS assessment_error,

aeas.row_id  as source_system_row_id,   
paas.source_system_row_id as paas_source_system_row_id,
paas.predictive_analytics_assessment_summary_id as paas_predictive_analytics_assessment_summary_id


from $$staging_schema.acx_ea_assessment_summary aeas
left join (select * from $$refined_schema.predictive_analytics_assessment_summary where predictive_analytics_assessment_summary_row_status
 = 'Active') paas
on aeas.system_id = paas.source_system_system_id 
and aeas.parent_id = paas.source_system_parent_id 
and aeas.cmm_container = paas.predictive_analytics_assessment_summary_type 
and aeas.id = paas.predictive_analytics_assessment_summary_row_source_system_key 
LEFT JOIN current_batch cb ON TRUE

where aeas.acx_ea_assessment_summary_row_effective_end_datetime = '9999-12-31 00:00:00.000' 
and aeas.acx_ea_assessment_summary_row_status = 'Active'
